  "text": "In the future, we will also test using a priori tropospheric delays obtained from ray-tracing through NWMs. The results of, for instance, [CITATION_1] and [CITATION_2] indicate that this can improve the results from the Intensives. The advantage of using ray-tracing, especially if a high-resolution NWM is used, is that also nonlinear horizontal variations will be modeled, not only the linear ones described by the gradients. Furthermore, we will study other potential error sources, such as the a priori EOP and unmodeled nonlinear station motions.",
